(C.D. 4771) Mitsubishi International Corporation v. United States Court No. 77-7-01146

Port of Anchorage

(Dated October 11, 1978) Bogle & Gates (David M. Salentine and Thomas J. McKey of counsel) for the plaintiff. *87Barbara Allen Babcock, Assistant Attorney General (Sidney N. Weiss and Madeline B. Cohen, trial attorneys), for the defendant.

ORDER

WATSON, J.

Upon reading and filing defendant’s motion for rehearing and reconsideration, plaintiff’s response thereto, and all other papers and proceedings had hereunder, it is hereby

Ordered that this court’s opinion and order of July 25, 1978 (C.R.D. 78-9) be, and hereby is, vacated; and it is further Ordered, Adjudged, AND Decreed that defendant’s motion for rehearing and reconsideration be, and hereby is granted, and that the above-captioned action be, and hereby is, dismissed for lack of jurisdiction.
